sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Row as SubscriptionRow onClick
    participant Navigate as handleNavigate
    participant SessionStore as sessionStore.setCurrentSession
    participant FetchTerminal as fetch /api/ide/create-terminal
    participant FetchBrowser as fetch /api/browser/focus-tab
    participant BrowserStore as useBrowserStore.activateSession
    participant TerminalStore as useTerminalStore.openFor

    Note over Row,TerminalStore: BEFORE — drive via raw fetch calls only
    User->>Row: click
    Row->>Navigate: onNavigate(project, session)
    Navigate->>SessionStore: setCurrentSession(target)
    Row->>FetchTerminal: POST /api/ide/create-terminal
    Row->>FetchBrowser: POST /api/browser/focus-tab

    Note over Row,TerminalStore: AFTER — drive via store methods (+ keep fetches)
    User->>Row: click
    Row->>Navigate: onNavigate(project, session)
    Navigate->>SessionStore: setCurrentSession(target)
    Row->>BrowserStore: useBrowserStore.getState().activateSession(sub.session)
    Row->>TerminalStore: useTerminalStore.getState().openFor(sub.project, sub.session)
    Row->>FetchTerminal: POST /api/ide/create-terminal (kept)
    Row->>FetchBrowser: POST /api/browser/focus-tab (kept)
